---
title: Turkish-Spiced Lamb Tacos with Garlic Aioli & Cucumber Salsa
description: We’ve given these tacos a little Turkish twist. These eye-catching handheld delights tick all the boxes – saucy mince, crisp
veggies, and our secret ingredient, chermoula spice blend, for loads of flavour!
